Swim registration is moving back online! Timmins Recreation Online launches January 2 - one website where you can book ice time, register for swimming lessons, view the availability of the City's rental spaces, request a booking, make payments, and more. You can create your personal or family account today and start to familiarize yourself with the site before it goes LIVE! Why? Because the next registration for private swim lessons is coming up in February and it's first come first serve ... and it can go fast. Save time and be ready to register! Here's the link: https://lnkd.in/gjSmQPmp Organizations, hockey associations, and sports teams will continue to register as usual. You do not need to make an account at this time. #timminsrecreationonline #timmins #registeronline #account
